---
import SidebarLayout from '../layouts/SidebarLayout.astro';
const title = "Welcome to Your E-Reader Jailbreak Hub";
---

<SidebarLayout title={title}>
  <details open>
    <summary>Unlock the True Potential of Your E-Reader</summary>
    <p>E-readers are wonderful devices... Jailbreaking removes restrictions and lets you personalize deeply.</p>
  </details>

  <details>
    <summary>The Philosophy Behind Jailbreaking</summary>
    <p>At its core, jailbreaking is about freedom and ownership...</p>
  </details>

  <details>
    <summary>Why Jailbreak Your E-Reader?</summary>
    <ul>
      <li>Install advanced reading apps</li>
      <li>Customize UI and fonts</li>
      <li>Access unsupported file formats</li>
    </ul>
  </details>

  <details>
    <summary>Risks and Considerations</summary>
    <ul>
      <li>May void warranty</li>
      <li>Can brick device if instructions aren't followed</li>
    </ul>
  </details>

  <details>
    <summary>Supported Devices</summary>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/kindle">Kindle</a></li>
      <li><a href="/kobo">Kobo</a></li>
      <li><a href="/pocketbook">PocketBook</a></li>
    </ul>
  </details>

  <details>
    <summary>Community and Resources</summary>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="https://www.mobileread.com/forums/">MobileRead</a></li>
      <li>Reddit: <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/kindle/">r/kindle</a> | <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/kobo/">r/kobo</a></li>
    </ul>
